products.title: Valencia Grey Taupe Roller Blind
products.metadescription:
Bring a little bit of the great outdoors into your home with this beautiful valencia grey taupe roller blind.  
A great accent for rooms with both grey or brown colour schemes, this warm stoney coloured blind will certainly give your house a snug and cosy atmosphere.
